title: CBS Login Timeout
solution: Restart the Synergy CBS service and check network connectivity.

title: Printer Not Responding
solution: Check printer connection and restart the printer. Ensure it is connected to the branch network.

title: Unitfund account opening not created for center
solution: त्यो केन्द्रको center fund account खुलेको छैन त्यसैले Client बाट center मा जाने कुन सेन्टर हो रोजेर Accounts मा जाने अनि माथि plus गर्ने .

title: Oracle Listener Not Running
solution: Start the Oracle listener service and verify database connection.
